<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Announcement - Bamboo Shop</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background: #f6f9fc; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; padding: 35px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border: 1px solid #eef2f6; }
    .header-banner { text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #f3f4f6; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 25px; }
    .logo-text { color: #2b7a0b; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0; }
    h2 { color: #111827; margin-top: 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; }
    .message-content { font-size: 15px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .footer-notice { border-top: 1px dashed #e5e7eb; padding-top: 20px; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5; }
    .footer-notice a { color: #2b7a0b; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    .btn-container { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
    a.button { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 32px; background: #2b7a0b; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(43, 122, 11, 0.15); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header-banner">
      <div class="logo-text">Bamboo Shop</div>
    </div>

    <h2>Dear Guest,</h2>
    <div class="message-content">
      {{message}}
    </div>

    <div class="btn-container">
      <a class="button" href="{{appUrl}}" target="_blank">Visit Our Store</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-notice">
      You are receiving this communication because you are subscribed to updates from Bamboo Shop.<br />
      If you wish to stop receiving these notifications, you can safely <a href="{{appUrl}}/unsubscribe?email={{email}}" target="_blank">unsubscribe here</a> at any time.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>